android.car.util.concurrent

接口 AsyncFuture<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - type returned by the Future.
    所有已知实现类:
    AndroidAsyncFuture

    public interface AsyncFuture<T>
    Custom Future that provides a way to be handled asynchronously.

    Note: it doesn't extend Future because it's implemented by AndroidFuture, which doesn't propagate Future.cancel(boolean) to the remote object.
